node.text:
Bringing the holiday mood dining to bed with @sprmrkt home delivery.
Yes, SPRMRKT is now offering uts expanded menu selection with the option of takeaway or islandwide delivery. You can also orders on the newly launched online ordering site, e.sprmrkt.com.sg.
I was happy cos SPRMRKT offers a variety of vegetable-forward creations while J gets to have some café-style favourites such as the Lychee Chiffon Cake. Best of all, I dun need to wash my juicer cos the restaurant also offers a good range of healthy healthy beverages.
